    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[Neural Rays for Occlusion-aware Image-based Rendering]]></title>
        <id>https://CDJ-happier.github.io/post/neural-rays-for-occlusion-aware-image-based-rendering/</id>
        <link href="https://CDJ-happier.github.io/post/neural-rays-for-occlusion-aware-image-based-rendering/">
